{"tid":895124,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[急] 唔見咗BNO，點續返?","createTime":"2018-11-09T02:54:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T08:55:35.000Z","uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ddc9b527ad56456a0c0fe736cc979c0a0c9ae3c2","tid":895124,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T02:54:48.000Z","msg":"講返我嘅情況先，我就95年出世，係唔係理論上我有得申請BNO嘅權利? 因為我唔肯定我細個有冇申請過BNO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果我想續番BNO，應該點做?有冇得向英國方面睇返我有冇得攞返BNO嘅權利?<br />\n<br />\n手上冇任何英國護照，BNO嘅屍骸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但有親戚係英國，唔知有冇幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nplease help<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce5dc350831ef5020d0c7ec602ac2b547b6f62f6","tid":895124,"uid":2445,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T02:57:32.000Z","msg":"無架啦喎 做中國人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f352d70aac6543103715a1bb4af141f465c841d3","tid":895124,"uid":77104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T02:59:01.000Z","msg":"去警署報失"},{"pid":"153fcebc0781f6cae15de1ffb783f8c8f3ca9036","tid":895124,"uid":470,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T02:59:40.000Z","msg":"比個標題呃左入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55caf39435fd3fa77c53d4b392ccff4ca28a433","tid":895124,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"153fcebc0781f6cae15de1ffb783f8c8f3ca9036","tid":895124,"uid":470,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T02:59:40.000Z","msg":"比